        <p class="catalog-kicker">Head-to-head</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title mt-5">Klaviyo vs Omnisend for Shopify email tools</h1>
        <p class="mt-7 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-9 text-[#4a2d17]">
          The practical fork for Shopify teams that outgrew Shopify Email but are not ready for enterprise retention ops. Klaviyo sells maximum Shopify data depth; Omnisend sells multichannel journeys without a six-week implementation. We compared both through a mechanical keyboard vendor, a specialty tea subscription line, and an outdoor climbing retailer — measuring newsletters, lifecycle automation, and push/SMS coordination as one buyer's catalog decision.
